## Color Palette Reference

| Token          | Hex       | Usage                              |
|----------------|-----------|-------------------------------------|
| body           | #533e27   | All body text, list markers         |
| heading        | #7c2c00   | H1, H2, links, strong, CTAs        |
| link-hover     | #b7714b   | Link hover states                   |
| accent-bg      | #faf6ef   | Card backgrounds, review cards      |
| accent-border  | #e8dcc8   | Card borders, dividers              |
| separator-bg   | cabin_separator.png  | Section dividers (bg-image) |
| cta-primary    | #7c2c00   | Primary buttons                     |
| cta-hover      | #8d3a00   | Button hover                        |

